stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> NavigateToAlerts
    NavigateToAlerts --> FetchAlerts : GET /api/alerts/
    FetchAlerts --> LoadingState
    LoadingState --> DisplayAlertTable : Success
    LoadingState --> ShowError : Failure
    ShowError --> RetryFetch
    RetryFetch --> FetchAlerts
    DisplayAlertTable --> ViewAlertRow : Browse alerts
    ViewAlertRow --> ClickAlert : Select alert
    ClickAlert --> NavigateToDetail
    NavigateToDetail --> [*]